==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Refined
<hw>Re*fined"</hw> <pr>(-f?nd")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Freed from
impurities or alloy; purifed; polished; cultured; delicate; as;
<xex>refined</xex> gold; <xex>refined</xex> language; <xex>refined</xex>
sentiments.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Refined</qex> wits who honored poesy with their pens.</q>
<rj><qau>Peacham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Re*fin"ed*ly</wf> <pr>(r<?/*f<?/n"<?/d*l<?/)</pr>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Re*fin"ed*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Refinement</ent>⟦br⟧
